{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6d79e98d5e","title":"戏赠周小丹联","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bfaf56a4db","index":0,"year":1936,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"6d79e98d5e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"01a0bf1731","type":"paragraph","text":"戏赠周小丹联！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6d79e98d5e"},{"id":"f01c07fba9","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年8月）江河移腾下；","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6d79e98d5e"},{"id":"fd4e8057c4","type":"paragraph","text":"蚂蚁做波臣回","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6d79e98d5e"},{"id":"9d23aafa73","type":"paragraph","text":"[111936年8月，周小舟从延安启程去新疆宣传抗日。新疆军阀盛世才心狠手辣，不好对付。临别时，毛泽东见小孩撒尿，触景生情，吟成这副对联相赠，鼓励他视困难，勇往直前。周小舟（1912-1966），湖南湘潭人，原名怀求，化名元诚、西笔，1937年由毛泽东改为现名。1935年加入中国共产党，曾任毛泽东秘书。建国后，曾任中共湖南省委第一书记。1966年“文化大革命”中因被迫害自杀。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6d79e98d5e"},{"id":"43bfd5af9e","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]跨，腰的两侧和大腿之间的部分。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6d79e98d5e"},{"id":"f88c6f73a5","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]波臣，指水族。古人设想江河湖海中的水族也有君臣之分，其被统治的臣仆奴隶，称为波臣。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6d79e98d5e"}],"page":{"id":"6ff00dccfc","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6d79e98d5e","start":103,"end":103}}}},"__N_SSG":true}